profile: Oxbow Electric is fully committed to providing our customers with the best possible electrical construction experience.  With our core values of reliability, professionalism, integrity, quality and safety we strive for perfection and detail until you are fully satisfied.  We specialize in residential, commercial and industrial services.  Whether you're in need of a small wiring fix, LED upgrades, small or large renovations, service upgrades or brand new builds both residential and commercial we get the job done right.  We are available 7 days a week and serve all of the Okanagan, Osoyoos, Oliver, Ok Falls, Penticton, Summerland, Peachland, West Kelowna and Kelowna.  We also serve Rock Creek, Grand Forks, Keremeos and Princeton.
